    question: "What types of furniture do you clean?",
    answer: "We clean a wide variety of upholstered furniture, including sofas, sectionals, loveseats, armchairs, dining chairs, ottomans, and more. Our cleaning methods are safe and effective for most fabrics, such as microfiber, cotton, polyester, linen, and blends.\n\nBefore cleaning, our technicians test fabric types to ensure the right products and techniques are used, giving your furniture a deep, refreshed clean without risk of damage."
